<p>
<h2>Biography:</h2>
<p>
Hong Xie is joining the Big Data Research Center at Chongqing Institute of Green and Intelligent Technology,
Chinese Academy of Sciences. 
He received Ph.D. degree in the <a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/">Department of Computer Science and Engineering</a> 
at <a href="http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/">The Chinese University of Hong Kong</a> in 2015, 
proudly under the supervision of <a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~cslui/">Prof. John C.S. Lui</a>.  
He received his B.Eng. degree from <a href="http://cs.ustc.edu.cn/">the School of Computer Science and Technology</a> 
at <a href="http://www.ustc.edu.cn/">The University of Science and Technology of China</a> in 2010.  
Hong Xie was a postdoctoral research fellow at 
<a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/v7/en/index.html">Department of Computing Science and Engineering</a>, 
<a href="https://www.cuhk.edu.hk/english/index.html">The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK)</a>  
hosted by <a href="http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~cslui/"> Prof. John C.S. Lui</a>,   
and a postdoctoral research fellow at 
<a href="https://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/">School of Computing</a>,  
<a href="http://www.nus.edu.sg/">Nationial University of Singapore</a> 
hosted by 
<a href="https://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/~tbma/"> Prof. Richard T.B. Ma </a>.  
He was also a faculty member at Chongqing University.  
He is a member of CCF, a member of IEEE and a member of ACM. 



</p>
<hr>


<h2>Research</h2>
<ul>

<li> <strong>Research interests:</strong>  
Data Mining, Machine Learning 
<br>
Particularly focus on desgning and analyzing data driven decision making models and algorithms for Internet applications 
such as recommendation systems, online social networks, cloud systems, etc. 
Currently, I am very interested in data driven decision making problems arising from AIOps (artificial intelligence for IT operations).  
</i> 
  
<li> <strong>Research outputs:</strong> 
<a href="https://hongxie.github.io/publication"> Publications </a>
</i>    

</ul>

 
