<h2>
<span style="color:red"><strong>Hiring@Big Data Research Center at Chongqing Institute of Green and Intelligent Technology,
Chinese Academy of Sciences</strong></span>
</h2>
<ul>
<li>We are looking for self-motivated faculty members, Posdocs, Ph.D. students, Master students and Intern students. 
Ideal backgrounds would be applied math/statistics, computer science, software engineering, electric engineering, etc., 
but they are not the prerequisite. 
Having experience in reinforcement/bandit learning, deep learning, AIOps, etc., would be a plus.  
You are encouraged to apply, if you are interested in machine learning and big data. 
</li> 
</ul>
 

